5/16
establish server to build a full-stack project
instruction at root file terminal:
mkdir server
cd server
npm init -y

in the server file:
npm install express cors dotenv
npm install -D nodemon
express = create backend API server
cors = allow frontend React investigate backend
dotenv = read .env environment varible
nodemon = restart server when developing

express() create a backend application
frontend need to send data with JSON format:
app.use(express.json())
backend receive data from req.body

req = request from frontend e.g. browser request
res = response from backend to frontend

res.json({status: "OK"}) :backend response this JSON format messgae to browser
